data.description: Discover a hidden gem in South Los Angeles! This exceptional Quadroplex unit is situated on one lot with two buildings and is an opportunity not to be missed. Whether you're a savvy investor or seeking a place to call home with rental income, this property has it all.  Two of the units have been thoughtfully updated, showcasing modern upgrades and a desirable two-story layout. The upstairs unit features, a spacious 2-bedroom, 1-bath layout with a dining area and a large living room, providing ample space for comfortable living. The downstairs unit offers 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, perfect for accommodating various living arrangements. Additionally, there are two covered parking spaces available for residents' convenience. Located in a prime location, you'll have easy access to various amenities, schools, parks, and transportation options. Don't miss out on this must-see 4plex. Schedule a viewing today and unlock the potential of this hidden gem!
